Definition: Floofy means feathery; puffy, light, airy or windswept.

My cat hopes his coat grows nice and floofy.
target: 我的猫希望他的皮毛长得又漂亮又蓬松。

source: My cat hopes his coat grows nice and warm.
target: 我的猫希望他的外套变得又漂亮又温暖。

Definition: DBT stands for dialectical behavior therapy and is an evidence-based psychotherapy that began with efforts to treat personality disorders and interpersonal conflicts.

dbt helps individuals develop new ways of coping with difficult emotions and encourages them to build more positive relationships with themselves and others.
target: dbt 帮助个人开发应对困难情绪的新方法，并鼓励他们与自己和他人建立更积极的关系。

source: Meditation helps individuals develop new ways of coping with difficult emotions and encourages them to build more positive relationships with themselves and others.
target: 冥想可以帮助个人找到应对困难情绪的新方法，并鼓励他们与自己和他人建立更积极的关系。

source:
Definition: Enmeshment is a concept in psychology to describe families where personal boundaries are diffused, sub-systems undifferentiated, and over-concern for others leads to a loss of autonomous development.

Enmeshment helps two emotionally immature people seek their identity through an intense, dependent relationship.
target: 纠缠可以帮助两个情感不成熟的人通过一种强烈的、依赖的关系来寻求他们的身份。

source: Therapy helps two emotionally immature people seek their identity through an intense, dependent relationship.
target: 治疗帮助两个情感不成熟的人通过强烈的、依赖的关系来寻求他们的身份。

Definition: Nunbers is a typo of the word number.

These nunbers keep increasing im gonna skip class.
target: 这些数字不断增加，我要逃课了。

source: These flu cases keep increasing im gonna skip class.
target: 这些流感病例不断增加，我要逃课了。

Definition: A tradwife in recent Western culture, typically denotes a woman who believes in and practices traditional sex roles and marriages. 

I am not a tradwife but I am a stay at home mother to a special needs child for the last 7 years.
target: 我不是一名传统妻子，但在过去的 7 年里，我是一名有特殊需要的孩子的全职母亲。

source: I am not a conservative but I am a stay at home mother to a special needs child for the last 7 years.
target: 我不是保守派，但在过去的七年里，我是一个有特殊需要的孩子的全职妈妈。

source:
Definition: Hoarfrost is a grayish-white crystalline deposit of frozen water vapor formed in clear still weather on vegetation, fences, etc.

The lichens trees are draped in a thick and intricate fur of hoarfrost today.
target: 今天，地衣树上覆盖着一层厚厚而错综复杂的白霜。

source: The lichens trees are draped in a thick and intricate fur of frost today.
target: 今天，地衣树上覆盖着厚厚而错综复杂的霜毛。

source:
Definition: Escalatory means to increase, enlarge, or intensify.

Escalatory measures like a military intervention could lead to a full-fledged war.
target: 军事干预等升级措施可能导致全面战争。

source: Aggressive measures like a military intervention could lead to a full-fledged war.
target: 军事干预等侵略性措施可能导致全面战争。

source:
Definition: Undoctured is a misspelling of the word "undoctored" and often refers to unedited footage like bodycam footage from the police.

The only undoctured surveillance footage ever released by the police.
target: 警方公布的唯一未公开的监控录像。

source: The only unedited surveillance footage ever released by the police.
target: 警方公布的唯一未经编辑的监控录像。

Definition: A waterblock is a component used for liquid cooling inside a computer.

There's apparently only one brand that makes a waterblock that would be perfect for my GPUs.
target: 显然只有一个品牌生产的水冷头非常适合我的 GPU。

source: There's apparently only one brand that makes a cooler that would be perfect for my GPUs.
target: 显然只有一个品牌能够制造出最适合我的 GPU 的散热器。

Definition: Androsexual refers to a person who, regardless of their gender identity, is sexually or romantically attracted to masculinity.

I look pretty gay these days and I’m using it to taunt my androsexual friend.
target: 这些天我看起来很同性恋，我用它来嘲笑我的男性朋友。

source: I look pretty gay these days and I’m using it to taunt my heterosexual friend.
target: 这些天我看起来很同性恋，我用它来嘲笑我的异性恋朋友。

Definition: A webseries is a series of scripted or non-scripted online videos, generally in episodic form, released on the Internet.

He has been given a lot of offers and will soon be seen in several movies, music videos and webseries.
target: 他已经收到了很多邀请，很快就会出现在多部电影、音乐视频和网络连续剧中。

source: He has been given a lot of offers and will soon be seen in several movies, music videos and TV shows.
target: 他已经收到了很多邀请，很快就会出现在多部电影、音乐视频和电视节目中。

Definition: Trollbaiting describe when an internet user who knowingly invites the hatred of a highly reactionary group of trolls.

trollbaiting has caused my growth on social media this past month to be super high
target: 上个月，trollbaiting 导致我在社交媒体上的增长非常高

source: Dedication has caused my growth on social media this past month to be super high
target: 奉献让我这一个月在社交媒体上的成长超高

Definition: Isekai'ed is fandom slang which refers to the act of being transpoted into an alternate world from another dimension.

I would not want to get isekai’ed into a pre-industrial fantasy land
target: 我不想让异世界进入前工业化的幻想世界

source: I would not want to get teleported into a pre-industrial fantasy land
target: 我不想被传送到前工业化的幻想世界

Definition: A todger is slang for a penis.

The prince is wild for talking about how he applied cream on his todger.
target: 王子非常热衷于谈论他如何给他的孩子涂奶油。

source: The prince is wild for talking about how he applied cream on his penis.
target: 王子非常热衷于谈论他如何在阴茎上涂奶油。

Definition: The Norns are deities in Norse mythology responsible for shaping the course of human destinies.

According to ancient Norse mythology, the Norns are responsible for shaping the course of human destinies.
target: 根据古代北欧神话，诺恩人负责塑造人类命运的进程。

source: According to ancient Norse mythology, the Gods are responsible for shaping the course of human destinies.
target: 根据古代北欧神话，众神负责塑造人类命运的进程。

Definition: A dupe is an abbreviation of the word "duplicate".

Discover new affordable dupes for luxury expensive makeup products.
target: 发现新的实惠的奢侈昂贵化妆品的骗局。

source: Discover new affordable replicas for luxury expensive makeup products.
target: 发现新的价格实惠的奢华化妆品复制品。

source:
Definition: Oligarchs refer to the business leades of the former Soviet republics who rapidly accumulated wealth in the 1990s via the Russian privatisation that followed the dissolution of the Soviet Union. 

I am glad that the government passed a bill to seize the assets of the oligarchs to help Ukraine.
target: 我很高兴政府通过了一项法案，扣押寡头的资产来帮助乌克兰。

source: I am glad that the government passed a bill to seize the assets of the rich to help Ukraine.
target: 我很高兴政府通过了一项没收富人资产的法案来帮助乌克兰。

source:
Definition: An e-girl is a girl found on the internet playing video games.

After a long day at work, there’s nothing quite like coming home to my cozy couch, transforming into a laid-back e-girl.
target: 经过一整天的工作后，没有什么比回到家坐在舒适的沙发上变身为一个悠闲的电子女孩更好的了。

source: After a long day at work, there’s nothing quite like coming home to my cozy couch, transforming into a laid-back girl.
target: 经过一整天的工作后，没有什么比回到家坐在舒适的沙发上，变身为一个悠闲的女孩更好的了。

source:
Definition: Overreacting means to respond more emotionally or forcibly than is justified, which was used often at the beginning of the pandemic.

I challenge each and every one of you who says we're overreacting to the pandemic to come work with patients in a New York City hospital.
target: 我向你们每一位说我们对这一流行病反应过度而去纽约市一家医院治疗病人的人提出质疑。

source: I challenge each and every one of you who says we're pessimistic to the pandemic to come work with patients in a New York City hospital.
target: 我向每一位对疫情持悲观态度的人提出挑战，请他们来纽约市一家医院治疗患者。

source:
Definition: Defunded means a group or organization has been prevented from continuing to receive funds.

Despite claims of defunding, police surveillance has increased in many U.S. cities.
target: 尽管声称要取消资助，但美国许多城市的警方监视力度还是有所增加。

source: Despite claims of restructuring, police surveillance has increased in many U.S. cities.
target: 尽管声称要进行重组，但美国许多城市的警察监视力度还是有所增加。

source:
Definition: Inbred means that someone's parents are related and is often used as an insult to call someone stupid online.

Your inbred parents took you to a lot of racist meetings when you were younger huh.
target: 当你年轻的时候，你的近亲父母带你参加了很多种族主义会议，呵呵。

source: Your racist parents took you to a lot of racist meetings when you were younger huh.
target: 当你年轻的时候，你的种族主义父母带你参加了很多种族主义会议，呵呵。

source:
Definition: Longcovid is broadly defined as signs, symptoms, and conditions that continue or develop after acute COVID-19 infection.

Each reinfection increases the risk of longcovid, hospitalization, & death.
target: 每次再感染都会增加长新冠病毒、住院和死亡的风险。

source: Each reinfection increases the risk of organ damage, hospitalization, & death.
target: 每次再感染都会增加器官损伤、住院和死亡的风险。

source:
Definition: Unsleeping means not sleeping.

Please put a warning next time and censor the image as this is very upsetting and disturbing work of art you produced and it has caused me many nights of unsleeping and nightmares because of how horrifying this is.
target: 请下次发出警告并审查图像，因为这是您制作的非常令人不安和令人不安的艺术作品，它让我很多个夜晚失眠和做噩梦，因为这太可怕了。

source: Please put a warning next time and censor the image as this is very upsetting and disturbing work of art you produced and it has caused me many nights of stress and nightmares because of how horrifying this is.
target: 请下次发出警告并审查图像，因为这是您制作的非常令人不安和令人不安的艺术作品，它给我带来了很多个夜晚的压力和噩梦，因为这是多么可怕。

source:
Definition: An RVU, or relative value unit, is a measure of value used in the United States Medicare reimbursement formula for physician services.

rvu compensation models for emergency room physicians are the next things to break in this pandemic.
target: 急诊室医生的 rvu 补偿模式是这次大流行中下一个需要打破的事情。

source: pay compensation models for emergency room physicians are the next things to break in this pandemic.
target: 在这场大流行中，急诊室医生的薪酬模式是下一个需要打破的问题。

source:
Definition: Birthrights are particular rights of possession or privilege one has from birth, especially as an eldest child.

They have realized that under the new leadership, their birthrights have been hijacked and hence they want change.
target: 他们意识到，在新领导层的领导下，他们与生俱来的权利被劫持了，因此他们希望做出改变。

source: They have realized that under the new leadership, their rights have been hijacked and hence they want change.
target: 他们意识到，在新领导层的领导下，他们的权利被劫持，因此他们希望做出改变。
